This video is full of false information and presuppositions promoted by other youtube celebrities like his buddy Chris Putnum, Steve Quayle, Chuck Missler, and Tom Horn.
His Age of Deceit documentaries are his claim to fame, boasting over 4 million views in total.
Great quality, massive production with some well known guests like Chris White who makes some really good videos himself like "Age of Aquarius, Age of Evil."
I give it 1 star because I believe it to be heresy. As much truth about the NWO as is presented in his prior works, this is apologetics for his bogus view on the sons of God in Genesis chapter 6.
A theory that first got it's start in Alexandria, which is currently held by gnostics, occultists, jehova's witnesses, mormons, catholics, and seventh day adventists as absolute truth.
I appreciate that he only uses the bible to explain his view, but what he does with Genesis 4:26 is absolutely wrong and heretical.
